name: WanSwap [OLD]
public_notice: WanSwap has recently migrated from their v1 contract to their v2 one. Visit this post for more information and visit the new token page here.
additional_notices: Kindly be aware of liquidity-related risks. This notice is not directed at any project in particular, and is more of a cautionary reminder.
